## filter()

`filter()` 方法创建一个新的匹配过滤条件的数组

**使用 for:**

```javascript
var arr = [
  {"name":"apple", "count": 2},
  {"name":"orange", "count": 5},
  {"name":"pear", "count": 3},
  {"name":"orange", "count": 16},
];
var newArr = [];
for(var i= 0, l = arr.length; i< l; i++){
  if(arr[i].name === "orange" ){
    newArr.push(arr[i]);
  }
}
console.log("Filter results:",newArr);
```

**使用 filter:**

```javascript
var arr = [
  {"name":"apple", "count": 2},
  {"name":"orange", "count": 5},
  {"name":"pear", "count": 3},
  {"name":"orange", "count": 16},
];
var newArr = arr.filter(function(item){
  return item.name === "orange";
});
console.log("Filter results:",newArr);
```


